.SH "Constructor & Destructor Documentation"
.PP 
.SS "panel::backend::VolumeControl::VolumeControl (QObject * parent = \fRnullptr\fP)\fR [explicit]\fP"

.PP
The constructor for \fR\fBVolumeControl\fP\fP\&. Initializes the PulseAudio threaded main loop and context, sets up the state callback, and starts the PA thread\&. Subscribes to all sink, source, sink-input, source-output, and server events once the context reaches \fRPA_CONTEXT_READY\fP\&. 
.PP
\fBParameters\fP
.RS 4
\fIparent\fP (QObject*) The parent QObject\&. 
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns\fP
.RS 4
void\&. 
.RE
.PP

.SS "panel::backend::VolumeControl::~VolumeControl ()\fR [override]\fP"

.PP
The destructor for \fR\fBVolumeControl\fP\fP\&. Safely disconnects the PulseAudio context, removes callbacks, stops the PA main loop thread, and frees all PA resources\&. 
.PP
\fBReturns\fP
.RS 4
void\&. 
.RE
.PP

